Dear,Thank you for taking the time to participate in our research. CMET is focusing on the microscopically small organisms that are omnipresent in our environment and even in our own body. To maximize the value of our tiny companions, we need your help!In 30 to 45 minutes of your valuable time we would like to get an idea about your lifestyle, health state and dietary habits in order to optimize preventive and therapeutic strategies to improve gut and overall health. Your contribution will enable us to personalize human gut microbiota research and besides completing the questionnaire, it will involve the donation of a faecal sample.Your participation does not entail any foreseeable risks. However, if you feel uncomfortable, you can withdraw from the survey at any point.This survey is in accordance with ethical approval issued by Ghent University Hospital. Instead of entering your name, we ask you to use a personal code. This code will be given to you and will only accessible by the researcher. As a result, your answers to the questionnaire are encoded and strictly confidential.If you have questions at any time about the survey or research, contact the CMET team at CMET.FFQ@ugent.beThank you very much for your time and support. Please start with the survey now by clicking on the Next button below.
